dataIdInfo.idPurp: Display spawning and rearing habitat for Salmon populations in the central valley.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Displays spawning and rearing habitat for Fall Run Chinook Salmon, Spring Run Chinook salmon, and Steelhead in the central Valley. For the methodology used to model spanwing and rearing habitats, see documentation on habitat modeling.

Modified from the original CVPIA dataset. Jack Slough and Best Slough added 2023-08-07 as additional rearing habitat.

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.
